# Blog Images

This directory contains blog post featured images.

## Recommended Image Specs

- **Dimensions**: 1200x630px (Open Graph standard)
- **Format**: JPG or PNG
- **File Size**: < 300KB
- **Naming**: Use lowercase with hyphens

## Images Needed

Based on sample blog posts:

- `fpga-synth.jpg`
- `solar-power.jpg`
- `pcb-tools.jpg`

## Tips

- Use high-quality images related to your post topic
- Can be photos of your work, diagrams, or relevant stock photos
- Free stock photo sources: Unsplash, Pexels, Pixabay
